Date: Fri, 13 Jun 2025 20:01:51 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 3/6] UPSTREAM: DP: wifi: ath12k: New Telemetry Objects and
 Macros

This patch introduces design changes to align Telemetry objects
with the new Data Path (DP) object model.

Design Changes:
- All peer-level per-packet path counters now reside at the
  MLD peer level with link granularity to enable efficient KPI access.
- All peer-level counters updated in HTT and Monitor paths are now
  maintained at the link peer level with link granularity.
Code Changes:
- Renamed dp_peer_stats to dp_link_peer_stats.
- Added new DP telemetry objects and macros for statistics updates.
- Introduced a new dp_peer_stats object for per-packet
  Tx completion counters.

Patch-dependency:
	0426-0002-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Move-HAL-enums-to-common-fil.patch

Signed-off-by: Kenvish Butani <kbutani@qti.qualcomm.com>
